ExperimentFileTableModel::ExperimentFileTableModel Synopsis:

An input list of CHP files can be given at the command line and if so is the file is read via the TsvFile object, in keeping with Affy practice.

Main constructor to read the file list and stash the data into the standard TranslationInputTsvTableModel.

Parameters:
rte - RunTimeEnvironment which contains options
probeSetFilterFileName - the input file to read.
